query:
SELECT carrier_site site,SYSTEM_ID,Round(CYCLE_TIME/60,1) ct,process_date,
--step_name,
SERIAL_NUM, CARRIER_SERIAL_NUM, PASS_FAIL,scrapreason, CH1_NUM_EPOXY_DOTS, comments, CH2_INITIAL_POWER_DBM, CH3_INITIAL_POWER_DBM, CH4_INITIAL_POWER_DBM,
CH1_CURED_POWER_DBM,CH2_CURED_POWER_DBM, CH3_CURED_POWER_DBM, CH4_CURED_POWER_DBM
FROM LR4_SHIM_ASSEMBLY
where step_name= 'TOSA SUBASSEM3 (SUBASSEM2, SI LENS)'
and process_date >= To_Date('2013-12-03 15:00:00','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')
AND process_date <= To_Date('2013-12-03 23:00:00','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')
AND PASS_FAIL = ('F')
ORDER BY process_date
